snippet.title: Just Dance.EXE - Announcement TRAILER | NEW Features
snippet.description:
Just Dance.exe will be released soon and finally here is the first trailer showing some new things! Stay tuned because during this month I will be uploading videos of just dance.exe showing new things about the game! 

If you have any doubts you can ask me in the coments bellow :)
